message.content:
logi: change btr-70k for either the brdm-2u or the bmd 2k

inf: Drop the bmp3 for sapery in btrt.  Sapery in btrt is simply too good not to take due to both the sapery part and the btrt part.

support: fine, but you may end up wanting the buk over the tor after a few playtests.

tank: I'd probably upvett the bv, but keeping it downvetted is understandable.

recon: drop the bmv for more gru in the btr90, and then upvett the razvedka.  I doubt you'll be needing more than 7.   If 2x gru in btr90 is too expensive, you can go GRU in the btr80a instead.

veh: I'd probably upvett the bmpt.  Afgansky has a shit salvo, so if you want a 2nd vehicle card, take either the 10 point zptu or the zhalo.

helo: upvett the akula, since you'll call it out so rarely that you want it to hit every time (missiles eat up a lot of supply), and I doubt you'll need more than 1

plane: With tor and tunguska + 2x btrzd, I don't think you'll be needing the PU.  You can replace this with a 25T.  Then, downvett your sead, since 2 per card is much much stronger than 1 per card.

repost when done

**Commit 23**(11.1.2023)
-3rd slot in german military high command bug fixed 
-naval speed advisor buffed 
-Generals can have maximum 7 traits now 
-Invasion penalty bonuses for conquering Africa and Pacific Islands lowered 
-Ethiopia cant take factory focuses until its fascist 
-Africa gives only 1% extra or less stats for barb when objective is taken 
-General attack skill 2.5% attack ---> 2% attack
-General defense skill 2.5% defense --->3% defense 
-Added support SPAA 
-Anti air  air attack increased by 2 and anti air guns by 3
-Jalu is no longer urban 
-CAS flies better at around 40% air superiority
-CAS damage lowered by approximately 8%

-Last Stand/Force Attack doesnt reduce org damage but increasese defense/offense by additional 10% 
-Japanese special last stand and force attack still reduces some org damage 
-Axis Africa ability now doesnt require desert fox trait and is available for all axis minors and it provides additional 10% extra strength

-PP advisor removed for now 
 
GER/ITA

-Udet nerfed by 5% cas efficiency
-Festung Deutschland makes all german airfields 2k big

SOV
-Gets more big airfields behind major cities if industry got evacuated 
-Starts with more supply behind major cities 


CHI
-Stats increase per state lost decreased
